{"tid":2375650,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"明報：分析公務員對宣誓或聲明的疑慮","createTime":"2021-01-22T07:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T02:48:13.000Z","uid":85582,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"af18b2d07721a0cd26191e33221891aaaf7e190f","tid":2375650,"uid":85582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T07:40:54.000Z","msg":"「簽定唔簽？」&mdash;&mdash;分析公務員對宣誓或聲明的疑慮（文：林緻茵）<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%96%87%e6%91%98/article/20210122/s00022/1611239199752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%2596%2587%25e6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20210122%2Fs00022%2F1611239199752&d=CT6PJiTX903K6YLxhzu4TQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=42eaaef0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%2596%2587%25e6%2591%2598%2Farticle%2F20210122%2Fs00022%2F1611239199752&h=5e56efe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%96%87%e6%91%98/article/20210122/s00022/1611239199752</a><br />\n<br />\n有人覺得宣誓只係一個簽名，我個心唔服從咪得，政府又講明唔簽即炒，所以都係照簽。<br />\n但簽呢份嘢會唔會係代表將來工會連發聲都違反咗宣誓呢？<br />\n睇下wtsapp點解要跪低，就係因為個個都唔妥協；成個政府有十幾萬公務員，假設三萬人唔肯簽，呢件事的發展會唔會可以有啲改變？ <br />\n你可以覺得咁諗係天真，不過做唔做又真係喺自己的手度。<br />\n<br />\n唔想係到批鬥咩公務員仲黃唔黃的問題，因為今日係政府迫人宣誓，我相信係黃的都唔會想簽，呢件事只係再一次證明自由係到收窄緊。<br />\n<br />\n如果唔想將來連social media 鬧下黑警同政府都要處分，求下你一齊唔好簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔簽，要人......"},{"pid":"3efa1dde8fe37fbbb3ac6f6ec9fadb890cd65834","tid":2375650,"uid":298477,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"唉 好sad <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簽完搵夠錢就快d 走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7794f6aa6ba40049a38b3e0fc492bfbc22a259d","tid":2375650,"uid":249162,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"3efa1dde8fe37fbbb3ac6f6ec9fadb890cd65834","tid":2375650,"uid":298477,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTi